The lawmaker representing Imo North
Senatorial District, Senator Benjamin Uwajumogu, is dead. Former Governor of Imo State, Senator Rochas Okorocha, who is representing Imo West Senatorial District in the 9th Senate, confirmed Uwajumogu’s death to journalists outside the Senate chamber on Wednesday. The late Uwajumogu was said to have slumped in the toilet while having his bath. He was rushed to a private hospital in Apo,  Abuja, where he died Details later. 